layout.house_prompt: An art gallery with three exhibition rooms, an office, a storage room, and a bathroom. The first exhibition room has two paintings on the wall and a bench. The second exhibition room has three sculptures on pedestals. The third exhibition room has a painting on the wall with a bench in front for viewing. The office has a desk with a chair and a computer. The storage room has shelves with crates. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

hallway.text_description: A modern minimalist art gallery entry hallway with clean white walls and simple wayfinding signage.

exhibition_room.text_description: A modern minimalist exhibition room in an art gallery with clean white walls, museum-style lighting, two paintings mounted on the wall, and a bench for viewing.

exhibition_room_2.text_description: A modern minimalist exhibition room in an art gallery featuring three sculptures displayed on individual pedestals with ample circulation space and museum-style lighting.

exhibition_room_3.text_description: A modern minimalist exhibition room in an art gallery with a painting mounted on the wall and a bench placed in front for viewing, with museum-style lighting.

office.text_description: A modern minimalist gallery office with a desk, a chair, and a computer workstation.

storage.text_description: A functional gallery storage room with industrial shelves holding crates, with clear aisle space.

bathroom.text_description: A compact modern minimalist bathroom with a toilet and a sink.
